## 10. Second-Brain Navigation

The second-brain at `docs/second-brain/` implements Andrej Karpathy's LLM Wiki pattern.

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `wiki/_INDEX.md` | Human-readable catalog |
| `wiki/_SEARCH_INDEX.md` | Agent-optimized keyword search table |
| `wiki/_LOG.md` | Chronological ledger of wiki operations |
| `wiki/_SCHEMA.md` | Canonical format rules (required before any wiki write) |
| `wiki/_improvement-queue/` | Self-improvement entries (one `IMP-*.md` per signal; status in frontmatter) |

Other zones: `raw_sources/` (unprocessed inputs), `artifacts/plans/` (immutable plans), `artifacts/specs/` (immutable specs).

